                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Don't forget that tash will stick no matter what and unless the cleric is TWINKED to the gills, this will put his MR in the negative. 
<br />

<br />

<br />
Animation up, dispell, dispell, dispell, dispell dispell, hit him 6 or 7 times. Then tash, then mana sieve, then slow. Now for the fun part. Dot him. forget nukes. keep him dotted. Then with the pet on him, use two color stuns and just keep stunning him. Forget mez, mez will lower your dps because the pet will back of. Just keep stunning him
<br />

<br />
1)color stun
<br />
2)color stun
<br />
3)tash
<br />
4)dispell
<br />
5)slow
<br />
6)dot
<br />
7)mana sieve
<br />
8)blind
<br />

<br />
Now ever once and a while blind him and you can take out the dot and put in your rune or DD spell. Just make sure of one thing. DO NOT GROUP WITH HIM!!!!
<br />

<br />
Make sure you are ungrouped. If you are grouped, he can use auto follow and beat on you even when blinded.
<br />

<br />
Keep him from being able to cast and you will win everytime.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=750403" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: red"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: normal">Arcady</span></span></span></a>
<br />
Officer of the <a href="http://www.mithrilankh.com/forums" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="color: blue">Mithril Ankh</span></a>
<br />
Follower of the Church of Umbra
