                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Wow, I can see that NO ONE here plays on a pvp server.
<br />

<br />
Ok, I'm from vallon zek, and I'll fill you in on some of the things other people neglected to mention.
<br />

<br />
For starters, dispells, ALL kind, are unresistable. Sometimes they do NOT dispell a buffer because its too high level for that dispell(for example cancel magic doesn't drop level 60+ buffers , unless its casted multiple times, etc).
<br />

<br />
In pvp, level advantage makes a HUGE difference. So you will need high sv magic to avoid having all of his spells land, about 200 should be enough(taking into account that 200 sv magic is low for pvp servers *cough*) .
<br />

<br />
Enchanters have the advantage of time, time is where we excel, mainly because of our mana taps and dispells, by 4-5 min(if the battle should last that long) it should be a breeze, you will have clarity, and he will be fully dispelled(no buffers) giving you a 7 mana regen per tick advantage, not only that, if you invest in wandering mind, you will steal 125 mana every 2 or so minutes, giving you an extra 6 mana or so per tick and draining him of almost any standing mana regen he could have.
<br />

<br />
However this is just half of the battle, after he is fully dispelled and oom, the problem will be, how to kill him, with 12 levels of disadvantage, you will find that most of your regular spells will be resisted a LOT.
<br />

<br />
I would say that keep a pet up (animation)at all times and that will slowly drain away his HP like a dot.
<br />

<br />
Oh yeah, don't forget to buy jaspers for rune 3, that will help out tons. 1 or 2 instant click buffer items would be very helpful for that fight but if you don't have any you should keep a fast casting buffer or two if he chain dispells you(run to the opposite direction until you have good distance(sow should be in the back so you should be able to outrun him)).
<br />

<br />
If his sv magic is low, then this whole point is useless, just tashan, dispell, mezz, nuke, mezz nuke, and so forth....</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />'I learned long ago to cover my back and attack from behind'
<br />

<br />
               -- Cidolfas Orlandu</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
