                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Strip his buffs, drain his mana, and cast Illusion: Fire Elemental.  That'll take care of his wimpy melee abilities.
<br />

<br />
As for his nukes, that depends on your MR.  If you have high MR, let him waste his mana nuking you.  If you don't have high MR, buff your MR and mez/stun him every time he tries to cast one of his slow-casting nukes.
<br />

<br />
The only thing tricky about beating a cleric in PvP at these levels is that they can take a while to kill since they can heal themselves fairly efficiently as long as they have mana.  Also, beware that they can cast two invulnerability spells (Divine Aura and Divine Barrier) so remember to watch for the INVULNERABLE messages.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=824212" target="_blank" class="postlink">Provender Moonshadow</a>, High Elf Phantasmist
