                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">The only cleric dots are undead ones; so to dot themselves, they must have a clicky or outside help</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Not exactly a clicky, more like, 10pp, to buy a crimson potion, an item specifically designed to defend players vs mesmerize.
<br />

<br />
Instant click,lasts 3 minutes, cannot be dispelled.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />'I learned long ago to cover my back and attack from behind'
